OL,3,CReform UK council boss stripped of
OL,4,Cmembership over racist post claims
OL,6,FThe Reform UK leader of Staffordshire
OL,7,FCounty Council has had his membership
OL,8,Fof the party revoked following claims
OL,9,Fhe posted racist remarks on social
OL,10,Fmedia.
OL,12,FIan Cooper, who was elected to the
OL,13,Fposition in May, allegedly called
OL,14,FSadiq Khan, the London mayor, a
OL,15,F"narcissistic Pakistani" and said
OL,16,Fmigrants were "intent on colonising
OL,17,Fthe UK, destroying all that has gone
OL,18,Fbefore".
