OL,6,FThe campaign group Hope not Hate
OL,7,Fclaims racist posts online were made
OL,8,Ffrom accounts with his name.
OL,10,FThe group said: "Reform UK's Cllr Ian
OL,11,FCooper has posted dozens of racist and
OL,12,Fbigoted posts to YouTube and X/Twitter
OL,13,Funder his personal accounts."
OL,15,FThe posts are alleged to have been
OL,16,Fmade prior to the May election - in
OL,17,FFebruary, Cooper allegedly called the
OL,18,FLondon mayor, Sadiq Khan, a
OL,19,F"narcissistic Pakistani".
