OL,6,F"Revoking Ian Cooper's party
OL,7,Fmembership on a technicality and
OL,8,Fallowing Peter Mason to remain as a
OL,9,FReform county councillor and cabinet
OL,10,Fmember despite his racist,
OL,11,Fmisogynistic homophobic and anti
OL,12,Fpolice social media posts shows that
OL,13,FReform still wants to sweep this under
OL,14,Fthe carpet.
OL,16,F"Nigel Farage needs to instigate an
OL,17,Furgent review of his entire
OL,18,FStaffordshire operation. This is the
OL,19,Fthird time since May this has happened
OL,20,Fwith a Staffordshire Reform councillor
OL,21,Fand that pattern cannot be ignored."
