OL,6,F"So I made a snap decision to go
OL,7,Fthrough due process. All I would say
OL,8,Fis it doesn't look very good.
OL,10,F"We expect our people to be truthful
OL,11,Fwith us, and if they're truthful with
OL,12,Fus we'll be honourable towards them."
OL,14,FA Reform UK spokesman said: "Following
OL,15,Fan investigation into the failure to
OL,16,Fdeclare social media accounts during
OL,17,Fthe candidate vetting process,
OL,18,FCouncillor Ian Cooper has had his
OL,19,Fmembership of Reform UK revoked."
